# Antigravity Global Configuration

## Directory Structure

```text
.gemini/
├── antigravity/           # Antigravity Desktop config
├── antigravity-cli/       # Antigravity CLI config
├── config/                # Common config (Plugin & MCP) for Antigravity family
├── skills/                # Custom Skills
├── GEMINI.md              # Global Shared Context
└── README.md              # This file
```

## Plugins

| Plugin        | Description                                     |
| :------------ | :---------------------------------------------- |
| `code-review` | Reviews the code changes on your current branch |
| `conductor`   | specify, plan, and implement software features |
| `security`    | finds vulnerabilities in your code changes and pull requests |
| `nanobanana`  | generating and manipulating images using the Nano Banana models. |

## Skills

Global shared skill contains under `~/.gemini/antigravity-cli/skills`
which symlink to `~/.agents/skills`


